{"tid":940242,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［分享吓］有冇人諗住就嚟轉工？","createTime":"2018-12-13T19:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T01:41:13.000Z","uid":43936,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d54d3834e36c8038e1ff609b2706cdfa0f10596","tid":940242,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:25:34.000Z","msg":"17FG第一份工做緊細公司<br />\n份合約下年一月尾完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但腦細好似覺得我會做落去<br />\n雖然學咗好多野，腦細對我都唔錯<br />\n但人工福利嚟講份工好閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n腦細仲成日同啲客講條team train得好好會搞得掂projects<br />\n其實成條team得我一個，佢又遲遲唔肯請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我驚我同佢講唔續約佢會心臟病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過去意而決，難就難在開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾啲信心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c3bd44acdf4bf7e3659a62f2e876106b5ecce1","tid":940242,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:28:36.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"2e618e31c8387bf949647b55da3e29ff840fe3e9","tid":940242,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a428cfc397bad3bc6ccde49476a975e2b22a88","tid":940242,"uid":111253,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:38:51.000Z","msg":"返工千祈唔好當自己咁撚重要，亦唔好對公司有感情"},{"pid":"ecd34311f21006070d277e31ddedfc5e90a580aa","tid":940242,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c3bd44acdf4bf7e3659a62f2e876106b5ecce1","tid":940242,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:28:36.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:41:22.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想快啲有出咗嚟做野幾年先有嘅灑脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e204f2b9865961c9329978575c866813eb76684c","tid":940242,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e618e31c8387bf949647b55da3e29ff840fe3e9","tid":940242,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8192dc61002252b3faa7df6d8f5ada07ee42e1bd","tid":940242,"uid":43936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3a428cfc397bad3bc6ccde49476a975e2b22a88","tid":940242,"uid":111253,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:38:51.000Z","msg":"返工千祈唔好當自己咁撚重要，亦唔好對公司有感情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:54:11.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我咁少經驗當然唔會覺得自己好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔做公司都好快會請到人<br />\n問題係佢又唔請人train吓<br />\n咩都旨意我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講唔出口，唔想佢發洩負面情緒係我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得好多人(包括我)第一份工都會驚會傷感情，好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6872dc453b3375a8e4c88a683ed3a41f5f24971","tid":940242,"uid":22283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:41:13.000Z","msg":"魚唔過塘唔肥<br />\n走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}